sources.title: Dead Aim (1975) WESTERN
sources.description:
Movie Class by PizzaFLIX: Shown at the 1971 Venice Film Festival as BURN, BABY, BURN, this film was shot in an unmistakably Spaghetti Western-style in Mexico and co-produced with an Italian studio.

Stars: Glen Lee, Venetia Vianello, James Westerfield 
Director: José Bolaños

In this stylish western, a father and his adopted son search for the things they most want in life; for the son it's love, but for the father it's gold.
